        "title_max_width_mobile": 0,
        "title_max_width_desktop": 600,
        "text": "<p>LifeSync, an Amphenol company, is a global, vertically integrated manufacturer focused exclusively on patient monitoring connections. LifeSync serves healthcare organizations and medical device OEMs by designing and manufacturing ECG, SpO₂, neuro and custom medical interconnects designed to support standardization, operational simplicity, and reliable performance at scale. </p><p>Through disciplined engineering, advanced automation, ISO-certified manufacturing, and FDA 510(k)-cleared ECG reprocessing, LifeSync delivers consistent quality, dependable availability, and more sustainable lifecycle management across clinical and OEM environments.<br/><br/></p>",
